    cnt = [0 for _ in range(N + 1)]
    p = N
    while p >= 0:
        s.append(p >> 1)
        p >>= 1
    f = [0 for _ in range(len(s) + 1)]

        f[i] = 2 * f[i - 1] + s[i - 1]
    res = N - sum((cnt[p] for p in range(2, N + 1)))
